snippet.title: Pixel Wars -- Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play on Steam for FREE during the Playtest: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2308470/Pixel_Wars/

Ready for a challenge? Test your strategy skills in an intense real-time battle with friends. With just enough units and buildings to keep it exciting, you can jump into online multiplayer games the moment that perfect Steam invite arrives!

Discord: https://discord.gg/v3BF9XQnck
